Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.67,0:02:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要…填寫現實世界的情報啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的多謝你處處幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.48,0:03:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係啦 反正乘坐「沙漠賽車」也挺有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.48,0:03:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(708,670)}Buggy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.58,0:03:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這個 你比賽的區域是哪一個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.28,0:03:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…F區
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,F區37號
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.63,0:03:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是同時報名的問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是F區
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.32,0:03:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,12號的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.70,0:03:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 就算碰上了也已經是決賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了是指什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:40.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能進到淘汰制預賽的決賽階段
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.84,0:03:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不論最後輸贏 都可以獲得正賽參賽資格
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 我們一起晉級正賽不是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:51.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.74,0:03:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 如果真的在決賽碰上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不會因為是預賽 而放水哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然 碰上了的話就讓我們盡全力比試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:15.41,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&H414285&\bord0}第三屆 預賽淘汰賽報名 已經全部結束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 以國外的遊戲來說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這遊戲的日語支持做的還真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.03,0:04:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明官網就只有英文而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然運營方「ZASKAR」是美國企業
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過在這個日本服務器的運營人員中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像也有日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過你也知道 GGO不管在日本還是美國的法律上都屬於灰色地帶了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為通貨還原系統吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對外的主頁上 都只有最低限度的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如角色管理 通貨還原所用到的電子錢包賬戶之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與遊戲相關的手續多數都只能在遊戲中辦理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢…好厲害的遊戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 與現實世界幾乎完全隔絕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也因為這 遊戲中的和現實中的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.52,0:05:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直判若兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.46,0:05:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…沒什麼 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多得去預賽會場了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏 就在這下面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.76,0:05:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.37,0:05:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先去更衣室吧 你也得先換上剛才買的戰鬥服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:53.04,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H62655F&\frz353.8\pos(839,160)}BoB3的準備時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:53.04,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H62655F&\pos(821,394)\frz355.1}還剩餘28分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 都是群亂來的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？亂來的傢伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那些嚇人的傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在開賽前30分鐘就在那秀主要裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不就像在說「請來針對我吧」一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是 光劍和「FN.5-7」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在自己的比賽開始之前再裝備比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.14,0:06:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼呢 你也得趕緊換裝了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是 不…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…那個…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.42,0:06:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都沒有做自我介紹…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.61,0:06:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…其實是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:06:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在才？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺有意思的名字嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.67,0:07:06.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男性？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？什麼？但是你明明…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.64,0:07:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧 男人？！就你那個造型？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別跟過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但…但是…接下來要怎麼做我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別跟過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:07:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…我沒什麼認識的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別跟過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.26,0:08:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:28.50,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H62655F&\frz353.8\pos(839,160)}BoB3的準備時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:28.53,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H62655F&\pos(821,394)\frz355.1}還剩餘10分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.29,0:08:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只跟你講最基本的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.23,0:08:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後我們就是對手了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別誤會了 我並沒有原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒計時為0時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.20,0:08:59.16,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&H2B2B2B&\bord2\3c&HD4C89A&}剩餘{\c&H0000FF&}09{\c&H2B2B2B&}分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.72,0:08:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裏的所有參賽者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將會與預賽第一場的對手將會被自動傳送到專屬的某個賽場
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賽場是1000m3的正方體空間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.65,0:09:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地形 氣候 時間都是隨機的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雙方將在至少距離500m的地方開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決出勝負後 勝者回到這個待機區域
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.54,0:09:18.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敗者將會被傳送到一樓大廳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便輸掉也不會隨機掉武裝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為F區有64人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贏五次就能晉級決賽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.64,0:09:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到正式比賽的出賽權
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就解釋這麼多 別問我問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大致懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.35,0:09:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要打到決賽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都教了你那麼多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.23,0:09:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後一點也想要教給你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你嘗嘗敗北子彈的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.29,0:09:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就期待一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.22,0:09:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過你沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果預賽都過不了我也別玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把高手全都殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.94,0:10:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估計今天是我們最後一次談話了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就報備一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是將要打敗你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.28,0:10:28.74,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(687,99)}詩音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詩音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是桐人 多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.94,0:10:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呦 詩音 怎麼這麼晚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.49,0:10:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還擔心你會不會遲到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 「鏡子」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(688,670)}Spiegel
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰到點閒事佔據了時間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得你不是不參賽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道礙不礙事 我是來給你加油打氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.61,0:11:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裏能看到大屏幕的實況轉播
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.30,0:11:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 閒事是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把對面那傢伙帶來這裏之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 我就是對面那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你好 初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是詩音的朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別被外表騙了 那傢伙是男的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫桐人 性別男
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男的？！就是說…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詩音真的很照顧我 各方面…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這麼說好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪裏照顧你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.67,0:11:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我不記得同意你叫我詩音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這麼冷淡嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.44,0:11:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼冷不冷淡的 我根本不認識你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都幫人家選裝備了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:11:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.09,0:12:05.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在開始第三屆Bullet of Bullets預賽淘汰賽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,參加比賽的各位玩家將在倒計時結束後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自動傳送到預賽第一場的比賽場地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝給位好運
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.19,0:12:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要打到決賽 聽到沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會轟飛你腦袋的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.32,0:12:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你都約我了 我怎麼能不赴約呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你這…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是有點玩過了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.77,0:13:02.47,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H5E5954&\fad(400,0)\frx354\fry14\pos(469,297)\frz345.3}準備時間：剩餘        秒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.77,0:13:02.47,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H5E5954&\fad(400,0)\pos(428,446)\frz347\frx342\fry10\org(430.415,420.8)}賽場：古代寺院遺跡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要殺掉所有高手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個女孩會不會是死槍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.31,0:13:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟…哪一個才是真正的詩音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.34,0:13:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裏想破頭也不會有結果的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在劍上過招的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 如果交火的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會得出什麼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.74,0:13:43.68,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\frz347.6\pos(803,292)\c&H393A37&}剩餘 {\c&H2D1FD9&}01 {\c&H393A37&}秒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,子彈也太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.52,0:14:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼打根本靠不過去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.67,0:15:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能靠這把劍防住幾槍的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是要彈開這種速度的子彈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.81,0:15:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須精確地預測子彈的軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我能行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.18,0:15:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,著彈線會準確地告訴我子彈的軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:54.87,Warning,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}(｀・ω・´)外挂模式开启(｀・ω・´)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒搞錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離這麼近的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…又犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這要人命的戰鬥還要再打4場…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詩音她在…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:18:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…真貨嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真貨…？什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.18,0:19:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看了…你比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.93,0:19:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你用了…劍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.98,0:19:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是又怎麼 又不違反比賽規則
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.32,0:19:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再問 一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.96,0:19:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…真貨嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.89,0:19:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙 認識我？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會有錯 我肯定在哪見過這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.63,0:20:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也像這樣面對面說過話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在哪裏…我到底在哪裏和這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個名字…那種劍技…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.96,0:20:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…真貨嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也…我也認識這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙跟我一樣也是SAO生還者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰…到底在哪見過…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.92,0:23:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 曠野的決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
